\r\nFeatures like testimonials, faqs, pricing tables, maps and more make Startup Pro our most flexible theme yet.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;","filter":true,"visual":true,"column-classes":"one-half"},"media_gallery-2":{"title":"","columns":2,"size":"full","link_type":"none","orderby_random":false,"ids":[5834,5835,5833,5836],"column-classes":"one-half"},"text-9":{"title":"Built-in support for some of the most popular plugins.","text":"<ol>\r\n \t<li><strong>Atomic Blocks<\/strong>\r\nPage-building blocks for the new WordPress editor.<\/li>\r\n \t<li><strong>Easy Digital Downloads\r\n<\/strong>The easiest way to sell digital products with WordPress.<\/li>\r\n \t<li><strong>Gravity Forms\r\n<\/strong>The easiest tool to create advanced forms for your site.<\/li>\r\n \t<li><strong>WooCommerce\r\n<\/strong>The world's number one eCommerce platform.<\/li>\r\n<\/ol>","filter":true,"visual":true,"column-classes":"one-half","column-classes-first":true},"media_image-10":{"attachment_id":5902,"url":"https:\/\/demo.seothemes.com\/startup-pro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/blog-11-1024x628.png","title":"","size":"large","width":1860,"height":1140,"caption":"","alt":"","link_type":"none","link_url":"","image_classes":"","link_classes":"","link_rel":"","link_target_blank":false,"image_title":"","column-classes":"one-half","column-classes-first":true},"text-10":{"title":"Built in support for the new WordPress editor and Atomic Blocks.","text":"Startup Pro comes with built in support for all of the new WordPress editor blocks and alignment classes, as well as the awesome Atomic Blocks plugin to give you even more freedom when creating posts and pages.\r\n\r\nWe've also taken an extra step and added custom styling and fonts in the admin area to match the front end.","filter":true,"visual":true,"column-classes":"one-half"}},"front-page-4":{"gts_widget-3":{"title":"What people are saying.","column-classes":"full-width"}},"before-footer":{"custom_html-5":{"title":"Ready to get started?","content":"E